Notes: Final game between Northwest and UM-Rolla as UMR leaves for the GLVC in 2005.
Final home game for Northwest senior Ashley Poptanycz.
Northwest goes on 18-4 run in the final 8:35 of the first half.
Northwest's Ashely Poptanycz records 7th double-double of year.
Game.Officials: Rich Choponis (Referee),  Ralph Edwards,  Robyn Weisbrook
